00:51:55.000 --> 00:51:58.370
And I would like to know a
little bit about the amygdala

00:51:58.370 --> 00:52:04.970
hijack and the response that
different teens may have.

00:52:04.970 --> 00:52:06.870
I have one team
when I think they're

00:52:06.870 --> 00:52:10.580
hijacked that goes angry, and I
