00:52:15.640 --> 00:52:17.098
There's a wonderful
book coming out

00:52:17.098 --> 00:52:19.630
by Dan Siegel called
"Brainstorms."

00:52:19.630 --> 00:52:22.030
It'll be out December 26.

00:52:22.030 --> 00:52:24.060
And it's about the
adolescent brain.

00:52:24.060 --> 00:52:27.320
It's actually written for
