00:52:39.440 --> 00:52:43.210
One is the system for
instant gratification, which

00:52:43.210 --> 00:52:46.860
surges ahead, and the other
is for delaying gratification,

00:52:46.860 --> 00:52:48.900
which lags a little behind.

00:52:48.900 --> 00:52:52.940
And so individual
teens may differ

00:52:52.940 --> 00:52:54.450
in the gap between
that circuitry,

00:52:54.450 --> 00:52:57.410
but I've heard a
definition of maturity

00:52:57.410 --> 00:53:00.415
as widening the gap
between impulse and action.

