00:53:22.590 --> 00:53:24.920
this really doesn't
apply much to us.

00:53:24.920 --> 00:53:28.360
We have cognitive problems that
cannot be corrected and have

00:53:28.360 --> 00:53:31.330
been heavily-- heavy
medication has been used.

00:53:31.330 --> 00:53:35.960
I'm on medications that
