takes a lot of work.

00:53:51.190 --> 00:53:53.920
And I was wondering if you have
any suggestions for epilepsy?

00:53:53.920 --> 00:53:57.560
DANIEL GOLEMAN: I'm not a
neurologist, not a specialist.

00:53:57.560 --> 00:54:01.500
