00:54:21.670 --> 00:54:24.210
They hit many different systems.

00:54:24.210 --> 00:54:27.540
And the brain still
remains plastic.

00:54:27.540 --> 00:54:30.300
So you can go to the
mental gym and see--

00:54:30.300 --> 00:54:32.331
